thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEL52YtO.png&h=2e7151d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"但要佢哋忍痛，唔好意思&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6f8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=092766e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"e1e9509666086d4d039004990cf71b777608c8d5","tid":1364224,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:46:03.000Z","msg":"各文職公務員，你仲唔出聲？<br />\n<br />\n我係一位對黑警暴行非常憤怒既媽咪。尤其是香港政府制度既不公，令佢地可以肆無忌彈踐踏我地既權利，市民面對佢地既暴行毫無招架之力<br />\n由我一位紀律部隊的親友口中得知，政府正為所有紀律部隊進行薪酬調整 Grade Structure Review GSR，上一次GSR已經是十年之前。而今次重點在於為警察大幅加薪，而且已經到達關鍵程序<br />\n我覺得我地一定要向GSR Committee 抗議，強烈反對為警察大加人工。個committee系成個review 入面係扮演「關鍵」角色，因為由佢地決定同向政府建議「加薪幅度有幾多」。 咁做係為左比黑警知道市民既憤怒，佢地既行為雖然得不到制裁，但市民仍有方法令佢地付出代價，而且阻止佢地加人工，亦遠比現存機制，能更有效令佢地受到驚嚇同懲罰<br />\n提交時間：2019/7/26 上午08:59<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilSecrets/posts/724166154679171?__xts__[0]=68.ARDkO4mmCYvfyFEvWCr2MLJSflhiZcRjDGRMsdj8QUxA-rlo7YDL1ThuIStxioFKifzO6ptpcfGlc7KQ-3vCUNa8o9Pbqb6jDKJCxZX82xEAntp5JT9j9zsIxGmv79zyA2jViazcYVmsK8OF47yYitBj1R7aq-WmlxtUrH8NOotY1int-bt-VDA8VIIUtumHIuaCKZrg8PZgFBO_RI02oo3Na-UnPAEKaCFMuYyJgIBeTobnp3kTp-kytBXBGxkUv8j2xJOhQO6cGtYkH3P7hkJjf605VZnLn7_TRUzT5boaVAZ8q9EzIIuMi9vnEfcgg-PqEjYQhazc4i4hUVfb9iq8IzscxDZzYoyFrP99QSpXRYnJ-VHPNgEV-MXoLVoT9y9EXhafVA0oCgBfNpclvxhZJ3pg8J0JxqinqMshbnR2_t0Wt21Y5FE6iAuNVysm5BbDj7FfqaZmCVM7ycl9aLo8cmELURAGnMbYwV8V7KayQ_TiYD8B2g4j8HRE4hxUbjUcmc8riTAr5-0MmYg&amp;__tn__=K-R[/url]\" data-sr